+### Crate sizing rule
+
+Every `src/` file in rbmp-core should be ≤ 500 lines. If a parser grows beyond that, split it. Example: `bgp/evpn.rs`, `bgp/bgpls.rs`, `bgp/flowspec.rs` are separate files, not added to `bgp/nlri.rs`.
